Time|EEST]]\n| utc_offset_DST = +3\n|coordinates        = {{coord|42|19|01|N|24|1|59|E|region:AR|display=inline,title}}\n|elevation_m          = 560\n|postal_code_type       = [[Postal codes in Bulgaria|Postal code]]\n|postal_code            = 4400\n|website                = \n|blank_name_sec1        = [[K\u00f6ppen climate classification|Climate]]\n|blank_info_sec1        = [[Humid continental climate#Koppen Dfb|Dfb]]\n|footnotes          =\n}}\n\n'''Slavovitsa''' ({{lang-bg|\u0421\u043b\u0430\u0432\u043e\u0432\u0438\u0446\u0430}}) is a village in located in the [[Septemvri Municipality]] of [[Pazardzhik Province]], [[Bulgaria]]. It is the birthplace of former [[Prime Minister of Bulgaria|Bulgarian prime minister]] [[Aleksandar Stamboliyski]].\n\n==References==\n<references />\n\n{{Septemvri}}\n\n[[Category:Villages in Pazardzhik Province]]\n\n{{Pazardzhik-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox settlement\n|name= Slavovitsa\n|settlement_type= Village\n|image_skyline      =\n|image_size          = 300px\n|image_caption       =\n|image_flag         =\n|image_seal         =\n|image_map          =\n|map_caption        =\n|pushpin_map            = Bulgaria\n|pushpin_mapsize        =260\n|pushpin_label_position =right\n|subdivision_type   = Country\n|subdivision_name   = {{flag|Bulgaria}}\n|subdivision_type1= [[Provinces of Bulgaria|Province]]\n|subdivision_name1= [[Pazardzhik Province|Pazardzhik]]\n|subdivision_type2= [[Municipalities of Bulgaria|Municipality]]\n|subdivision_name2= [[Septemvri Municipality|Septemvri]]\n|leader_title       =\n|leader_name        =\n|established_title  = Established\n|established_date   = \n|area_magnitude     =\n|area_total_km2         = \n|area_land_km2          =\n|area_water_km2         =\n|population_as_of   = 2016\n|population_footnotes    =<ref>{{cite web|title=\u0422\u0430\u0431\u043b\u0438\u0446\u0430 \u043d\u0430 \u043d\u0430\u0441\u0435\u043b\u0435\u043d\u0438\u0435\u0442\u043e \u043f\u043e \u043f\u043e\u0441\u0442\u043e\u044f\u